1
00:00:07,725 --> 00:00:11,711
♪I found a faint light
in the fading dusk♪

2
00:00:11,712 --> 00:00:15,311
♪And met your steady gaze♪

3
00:00:15,312 --> 00:00:24,132
♪One knowing glance,
and side by side we walk on♪

4
00:00:24,575 --> 00:00:27,061
♪Longing finds no place to rest♪

5
00:00:27,062 --> 00:00:29,211
♪Through drifting wind and rain♪

6
00:00:29,212 --> 00:00:32,699
♪You are the prayer within my hands♪

7
00:00:32,700 --> 00:00:40,324
♪A single second frozen,
tears in focus, my heart already knows♪

8
00:00:40,325 --> 00:00:42,786
♪We made a promise long ago♪

9
00:00:42,787 --> 00:00:44,786
♪For all our days to come♪

10
00:00:44,787 --> 00:00:48,449
♪You are the fate I cannot outrun♪

11
00:00:48,450 --> 00:00:53,836
♪How much must I let go
to trade for one moment?♪

12
00:00:53,837 --> 00:00:56,457
♪Holding you close♪

13
00:00:56,637 --> 00:00:58,874
♪Would that be enough?♪

14
00:00:58,875 --> 00:00:59,659
=Echoes of Love=

15
00:00:59,660 --> 00:01:01,499
(Adapted from the signed screenplay
Echoes of Love on Migu Reading)

16
00:01:01,500 --> 00:01:03,682
=Episode 13=

17
00:01:04,339 --> 00:01:06,700
Not long after the Duchess
founded the Shengtang Guild,

18
00:01:07,100 --> 00:01:09,338
she contracted a venereal disease
and hanged herself.

19
00:01:09,339 --> 00:01:10,739
Do you not think all of this

20
00:01:10,740 --> 00:01:12,299
is a little too coincidental?

21
00:01:12,339 --> 00:01:14,659
But this scandal
has long been settled as fact.

22
00:01:15,540 --> 00:01:16,780
Even if you investigate,

23
00:01:17,059 --> 00:01:18,058
what could you change?

24
00:01:18,059 --> 00:01:20,299
Yet no one ever
saw her in an illicit affair.

25
00:01:21,180 --> 00:01:22,620
Without evidence,

26
00:01:22,979 --> 00:01:24,019
she would be just like us,

27
00:01:24,020 --> 00:01:25,620
judged by the world,

28
00:01:25,660 --> 00:01:27,739
forced to bear undeserved disgrace,

29
00:01:27,740 --> 00:01:29,459
perhaps even driven to her death.

30
00:01:31,580 --> 00:01:33,539
If we are
to uncover the one behind this,

31
00:01:34,180 --> 00:01:35,659
the Duchess' death

32
00:01:36,020 --> 00:01:37,539
may be a point of breakthrough.

33
00:01:38,180 --> 00:01:39,379
In your view...

34
00:01:40,900 --> 00:01:43,179
We can only begin
with the venereal disease.

35
00:01:57,979 --> 00:01:59,459
I am sorry, Gu Chengye.

36
00:01:59,460 --> 00:02:00,700
I came too late.

37
00:02:04,580 --> 00:02:06,379
Who told you to come here
and cause trouble?

38
00:02:06,779 --> 00:02:07,620
Leave now.

39
00:02:07,660 --> 00:02:08,859
Get up.

40
00:02:10,700 --> 00:02:11,979
Song Zhiyun,

41
00:02:12,180 --> 00:02:13,819
this is my family matter.

42
00:02:14,260 --> 00:02:15,620
It has nothing to do with you.

43
00:02:16,099 --> 00:02:17,300
A family matter?

44
00:02:18,260 --> 00:02:20,060
If this concerns your safety,

45
00:02:20,060 --> 00:02:21,760
how can you say
it has nothing to do with me?

46
00:02:23,580 --> 00:02:24,859
I, Song Zhiyun,

47
00:02:24,860 --> 00:02:26,699
am not one to stand aside.

48
00:02:28,939 --> 00:02:30,060
Get up.

49
00:02:31,180 --> 00:02:32,500
You shameless woman,

50
00:02:33,180 --> 00:02:34,899
how dare you walk
into the trap yourself.

51
00:02:34,900 --> 00:02:36,180
Seize her.

52
00:02:36,860 --> 00:02:37,979
Gu Chengye.

53
00:02:38,379 --> 00:02:39,699
What would I not dare?

54
00:02:39,980 --> 00:02:41,099
Duke Yu,

55
00:02:41,262 --> 00:02:42,503
this time,

56
00:02:42,539 --> 00:02:44,900
I have come expressly
to clear the Duchess' name.

57
00:02:46,539 --> 00:02:47,780
Clear her name?

58
00:02:48,180 --> 00:02:49,460
What do you mean?

59
00:02:54,837 --> 00:02:55,677
Back then,

60
00:02:56,099 --> 00:02:57,938
you insisted the Duchess

61
00:02:57,939 --> 00:03:00,357
was immoral and had contracted
a venereal disease.

62
00:03:00,539 --> 00:03:02,840
Yet she was a woman
who never stepped outside.

63
00:03:02,840 --> 00:03:05,400
How could she possibly have had
the chance to contract such an illness?

64
00:03:05,700 --> 00:03:06,620
So,

65
00:03:06,900 --> 00:03:08,778
last night, I deliberately sought out

66
00:03:08,779 --> 00:03:10,900
the physician who diagnosed
Lady Gu in those years.

67
00:03:11,980 --> 00:03:13,538
He said the Duchess at the time

68
00:03:13,539 --> 00:03:15,419
developed red rashes
and a persistent fever.

69
00:03:15,675 --> 00:03:16,859
These symptoms,

70
00:03:16,860 --> 00:03:18,857
though somewhat similar
to a venereal disease,

71
00:03:18,980 --> 00:03:21,457
followed an entirely different course.

72
00:03:21,860 --> 00:03:23,259
Yet, Duke Yu,

73
00:03:23,580 --> 00:03:25,819
in order to preserve
your so-called reputation,

74
00:03:25,819 --> 00:03:28,945
you did not allow the physician to examine her
before hastily reaching a conclusion.

75
00:03:29,939 --> 00:03:31,780
What exactly are you saying?

76
00:03:32,339 --> 00:03:33,580
After making extensive inquiries,

77
00:03:33,600 --> 00:03:35,086
I learned that
in the autumn of that year

78
00:03:35,087 --> 00:03:36,899
you led troops
on a campaign for three months.

79
00:03:36,900 --> 00:03:37,979
After you returned,

80
00:03:37,980 --> 00:03:39,420
Lady Gu fell ill.

81
00:03:39,659 --> 00:03:41,819
Is that not suspicious?

82
00:03:42,140 --> 00:03:43,780
What are you implying?

83
00:03:45,580 --> 00:03:46,658
You are slandering the Duke.

84
00:03:46,659 --> 00:03:47,780
Do you know?

85
00:03:50,659 --> 00:03:51,620
Insolent child,

86
00:03:51,700 --> 00:03:53,259
are you trying to rebel?

87
00:03:54,099 --> 00:03:55,419
In the fourteenth year of Shaoyuan,

88
00:03:55,625 --> 00:03:57,460
Duke Yu led troops north,

89
00:03:57,860 --> 00:03:59,300
and fought at Haoyuan.

90
00:03:59,659 --> 00:04:01,657
After three grueling months,
he returned victorious.

91
00:04:02,059 --> 00:04:04,498
As for the Duchess,
she had long lived in Jiangnan,

92
00:04:04,499 --> 00:04:06,145
never once exposed to wormwood.

93
00:04:06,650 --> 00:04:08,419
You were among wormwood every day.

94
00:04:08,580 --> 00:04:09,580
When you came back,

95
00:04:09,700 --> 00:04:11,419
pollen could easily have clung to you.

96
00:04:11,659 --> 00:04:13,859
That would have triggered
Lady Gu's allergy,

97
00:04:13,900 --> 00:04:15,300
causing red rashes

98
00:04:15,460 --> 00:04:16,820
that would not subside.

99
00:04:17,779 --> 00:04:18,659
In this book,

100
00:04:18,820 --> 00:04:20,419
it clearly records
the differences between

101
00:04:20,659 --> 00:04:22,459
venereal disease and wormwood allergy.

102
00:04:22,460 --> 00:04:23,170
(Compendium of Difficult Ailments)

103
00:04:27,437 --> 00:04:29,770
(Venereal disease: dryness of skin and blood,
lesions like grains of rice that bleed when broken)

104
00:04:30,299 --> 00:04:32,020
That is only your conjecture.

105
00:04:32,659 --> 00:04:33,900
There is no proof.

106
00:04:34,580 --> 00:04:36,099
I have no proof,

107
00:04:36,339 --> 00:04:39,179
but neither do you have proof she went out
and contracted such a disease.

108
00:04:39,580 --> 00:04:40,700
Think about it.

109
00:04:40,779 --> 00:04:42,539
If there had been a physician then

110
00:04:42,739 --> 00:04:44,338
to examine her carefully,

111
00:04:44,339 --> 00:04:45,739
to treat her properly,

112
00:04:46,140 --> 00:04:48,460
would she have suffered such injustice?

113
00:04:49,700 --> 00:04:51,236
On mere hearsay,

114
00:04:51,237 --> 00:04:53,197
you ruined Lady Gu's reputation.

115
00:04:53,737 --> 00:04:55,953
She took her life
to prove her innocence.

116
00:04:56,562 --> 00:04:58,723
Do you feel no remorse at all?

117
00:05:00,060 --> 00:05:01,460
Even so...

118
00:05:01,700 --> 00:05:03,299
Even so,

119
00:05:05,739 --> 00:05:07,895
you are a woman
from the pleasure quarters,

120
00:05:08,859 --> 00:05:10,580
who enticed the Duke's son.

121
00:05:11,025 --> 00:05:12,778
That alone is a capital crime.

122
00:05:12,779 --> 00:05:13,978
I came today

123
00:05:13,979 --> 00:05:15,659
with no intention of living.

124
00:05:15,979 --> 00:05:17,499
I only wish to trade my life

125
00:05:17,659 --> 00:05:20,259
for Lady Gu to have her spirit tablet
brought into the manor,

126
00:05:20,260 --> 00:05:21,780
a stele erected in her honor,

127
00:05:21,979 --> 00:05:23,460
and her name restored.

128
00:05:24,125 --> 00:05:25,380
Oh, by the way,

129
00:05:25,539 --> 00:05:26,579
on my way here,

130
00:05:26,580 --> 00:05:29,419
I happened to pass beneath the bridge
and met a storyteller.

131
00:05:29,475 --> 00:05:31,224
I told him everything.

132
00:05:31,975 --> 00:05:33,214
If I die,

133
00:05:33,299 --> 00:05:34,459
I fear this matter

134
00:05:34,460 --> 00:05:35,979
will spread on its own.

135
00:05:36,150 --> 00:05:37,499
Are you threatening me?

136
00:05:37,500 --> 00:05:38,380
I would not dare.

137
00:05:38,775 --> 00:05:39,855
It is only that

138
00:05:41,500 --> 00:05:43,419
I cannot bear to see
the one I care about

139
00:05:44,179 --> 00:05:45,419
in sorrow.

140
00:05:47,140 --> 00:05:48,299
Father,

141
00:05:49,580 --> 00:05:52,059
Mother loved you with all her heart,

142
00:05:53,060 --> 00:05:55,659
yet in the end she was left disgraced,

143
00:05:56,500 --> 00:05:58,499
and died under false accusation.

144
00:05:59,512 --> 00:06:00,792
It was you.

145
00:06:02,460 --> 00:06:04,140
You harmed her.

146
00:06:04,779 --> 00:06:06,580
You cared only for your reputation.

147
00:06:07,179 --> 00:06:09,557
You feared your own downfall.

148
00:06:10,580 --> 00:06:12,780
So Mother had no choice but to die

149
00:06:13,460 --> 00:06:15,780
to clear the Gu family's name.

150
00:06:17,739 --> 00:06:19,659
Was this bloodstained innocence

151
00:06:20,437 --> 00:06:22,420
enough to satisfy you?

152
00:06:26,437 --> 00:06:28,682
(Compendium of Difficult Ailments)

153
00:06:33,060 --> 00:06:35,499
I am not as weak as you.

154
00:06:36,339 --> 00:06:38,659
Nor am I as blind to right and wrong.

155
00:06:39,260 --> 00:06:40,580
As for her,

156
00:06:41,380 --> 00:06:43,220
I swear to protect her to the end,

157
00:06:44,339 --> 00:06:45,979
in life or in death.

158
00:06:47,339 --> 00:06:48,859
I will remain by her side,

159
00:06:51,250 --> 00:06:52,650
never to abandon her.

160
00:07:05,000 --> 00:07:06,201
Ye,

161
00:07:08,539 --> 00:07:10,260
take care of yourself.

162
00:07:11,700 --> 00:07:13,824
♪Night rain falls before the courtyard♪

163
00:07:13,825 --> 00:07:18,574
♪Illuminating the partings
of the mortal world♪

164
00:07:18,575 --> 00:07:22,338
♪Strangers meet again,
the past ablaze in vivid hues♪

165
00:07:22,339 --> 00:07:23,499
Song Zhiyun,

166
00:07:25,739 --> 00:07:26,799
thank you.

167
00:07:26,800 --> 00:07:29,415
♪A sharp arrow pierces through memory♪

168
00:07:29,460 --> 00:07:30,979
This is not your fault.

169
00:07:32,179 --> 00:07:34,700
The wronged should never feel ashamed.

170
00:07:36,659 --> 00:07:37,780
Thank you.

171
00:07:39,762 --> 00:07:42,820
♪After endless sorrow endured,
love is a word too hard to sever♪

172
00:07:49,339 --> 00:07:50,460
Report, sir.

173
00:07:50,962 --> 00:07:53,122
I have learned
the whereabouts of that performer.

174
00:07:53,380 --> 00:07:54,619
She is at the Gu residence.

175
00:07:57,940 --> 00:08:01,098
One is the Commander
of the Imperial Guard,

176
00:08:01,099 --> 00:08:03,499
the other a key witness.

177
00:08:03,580 --> 00:08:06,900
They must not be allowed to join forces.

178
00:08:08,460 --> 00:08:09,700
When the time comes,

179
00:08:10,580 --> 00:08:13,499
we will set them against each other.

180
00:08:14,580 --> 00:08:18,820
Take something
to the Gu residence for me.

181
00:08:19,659 --> 00:08:20,659
A wise plan, sir.

182
00:08:21,912 --> 00:08:27,807
(Spirit Tablet of the Gu)

183
00:08:39,837 --> 00:08:44,057
(Spirit Tablet of the Gu)

184
00:08:56,260 --> 00:08:57,379
Mother,

185
00:08:58,380 --> 00:09:00,540
the disgrace you bore all these years

186
00:09:00,900 --> 00:09:02,779
has finally been cleared.

187
00:09:03,980 --> 00:09:06,060
All of this is thanks to one person.

188
00:09:07,059 --> 00:09:08,499
Her name is Song Zhiyun.

189
00:09:09,740 --> 00:09:11,499
I do not know since when,

190
00:09:12,299 --> 00:09:13,820
but it feels as though

191
00:09:13,939 --> 00:09:15,899
she is everywhere in my world.

192
00:09:16,179 --> 00:09:18,899
I once did not believe
true feeling existed.

193
00:09:19,740 --> 00:09:21,019
But now...

194
00:09:26,980 --> 00:09:27,739
Mother,

195
00:09:28,050 --> 00:09:29,660
may you, in the afterlife,

196
00:09:30,225 --> 00:09:32,379
watch over us and keep us safe.

197
00:09:43,140 --> 00:09:44,340
(Maybe)

198
00:09:44,459 --> 00:09:46,899
(I truly misunderstood him.)

199
00:09:46,900 --> 00:09:48,178
(It seems)

200
00:09:48,179 --> 00:09:49,979
(he has nothing to do
with the Shengtang Guild.)

201
00:09:51,062 --> 00:09:52,222
Official.

202
00:09:55,539 --> 00:09:56,420
Official,

203
00:09:56,699 --> 00:09:58,600
the Shengtang Guild
has sent an invitation.

204
00:09:58,600 --> 00:10:00,259
They request a meeting
to discuss matters in detail.

205
00:10:00,260 --> 00:10:05,507
(Shengtang respectfully invites you)

206
00:10:06,380 --> 00:10:07,499
Send a reply.

207
00:10:07,939 --> 00:10:09,899
Tell them I will arrive on time.

208
00:10:10,380 --> 00:10:11,259
Yes.

209
00:10:17,539 --> 00:10:18,979
This is a lethal poison.

210
00:10:19,939 --> 00:10:21,979
If he refuses
to hand over the Beauty Portrait,

211
00:10:23,539 --> 00:10:25,259
then do not give him the antidote.

212
00:10:35,900 --> 00:10:37,060
What is it?

213
00:10:38,100 --> 00:10:38,979
Hesitating?

214
00:10:40,980 --> 00:10:42,820
Have you developed feelings for him?

215
00:10:48,179 --> 00:10:49,499
(Gu Chengye.)

216
00:10:50,059 --> 00:10:52,499
(You secretly consort
with the Shengtang Guild)

217
00:10:53,059 --> 00:10:55,379
(while pretending sincerity before me.)

218
00:10:56,100 --> 00:10:57,460
(If that is the case,)

219
00:10:58,299 --> 00:11:00,580
(then do not blame me
for showing no mercy.)
